<chapter xml:id="manual.scanner">
<title>Scanning</title>
<para>The Baofeng UV-5R features a built in scanner for the VHF and UHF bands. At </para>
<para>To enable the scanner, press and hold the
	<inlinemediaobject>
		<imageobject>
			<imagedata contentdepth="0.9em" format="png" fileref="figs/key-star.svg.png"/>
		</imageobject>
	</inlinemediaobject>
	key for about two seconds. This also works when listening to broadcast FM.</para>

<para>press and hold [star] to scan</para>
<para>in frequency mode it will scan in menu1 steps</para>
<para>in memory mode it will scan your channels</para>
<section>
	<title>Scanning modes</title>
	<para>There are three me</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>Setting scanner mode</title>
		<step>
			<para>Press the
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata contentdepth="0.9em" format="png" fileref="figs/key-menu.svg.png"/>
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject>
				key to enter the menu.</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>Enter
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata contentdepth="0.9em" format="png" fileref="figs/key-1.svg.png"/>
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject>
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata contentdepth="0.9em" format="png" fileref="figs/key-8.svg.png"/>
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject>
				on your numeric keypad to come to scanner mode.</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>Press
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata contentdepth="0.9em" format="png" fileref="figs/key-menu.svg.png"/>
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject>
				key to select.</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>Use the
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata contentdepth="0.9em" format="png" fileref="figs/key-up.svg.png"/>
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject>
				and
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata contentdepth="0.9em" format="png" fileref="figs/key-down.svg.png"/>
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject>
				keys to select scanning mode.</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>Press
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata contentdepth="0.9em" format="png" fileref="figs/key-menu.svg.png"/>
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject>
				to confirm and save.</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>Press 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata contentdepth="0.9em" format="png" fileref="figs/key-exit.svg.png"/>
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject>
				to exit the menu.</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
